      <article id="post-1837" class="post-1837 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-vr" role="article"> 
       <div class="singlebox"> 
        <div itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/WebPage" id="crumbs"> 
         <a itemprop="breadcrumb" href="http://www.vrlei.com">首页</a> &raquo; 
         <a itemprop="breadcrumb" href="http://www.vrlei.com/category/vr%e8%b5%84%e8%ae%af/">VR资讯</a> &raquo; 
         <span class="current">三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！</span>
        </div> 
        <header class="article-header"> 
         <h1 class="post-title">三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！</h1> 
         <div id="post-meta"> 
          <p class="post-meta vsmall"> <span class="post-meta-date">发表于 2016年4月13日</span> <span class="post-meta-author"> <a href="http://www.vrlei.com/author/vrvisitor/" title="">VR观察者 </a></span> <span class="post-meta-comments"><span><span class="screen-reader-text">三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！</span>已关闭评论</span></span> </p> 
          <div class="clear"></div> 
         </div> 
        </header> 
        <!-- end header --> 
        <section class="entry-content clearfix"> 
         <p>VR概念被炒作到红得发紫，两周前忍不住买了一个三块钱的VR简单体验。虽然产品Low到爆，但体验还是非常吸引人的(你不尝试的话，永远不知道VR有多神奇)。</p> 
         <p>进坑容易出坑难，今天小编又淘到了尚未在国内开卖的三星Gear VR，进行更深度一点的一眼，分享给大家。</p> 
         <p>Gear VR是三星旗下首款VR头盔，很多人听过，但印象并不深。因为它名气不小，但是并未在国内推广发售。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/9802cfcb1f89d9a4a9675e195a554a7b.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/9802cfcb1f89d9a4a9675e195a554a7b.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">Gear VR</span></p> 
         <p>　　Gear VR海外售价99美元，属于手机式VR(没有屏幕，需要插手机显示内容)，目前只能搭配三星S6/S6 Edge/Note 5及之后的三星旗舰手机，局限性大，体验成本相对较高。但一分钱一分货，总的来说这些钱花的值！</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/166e991578531ccc6459ff7d761a7565.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/166e991578531ccc6459ff7d761a7565.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">Gear VR</span></p> 
         <p><strong>　　基本原理：</strong></p> 
         <p>Gear VR和市面上售价几十块的VR头盔原理一样，显示画面在手机端，靠手机分屏将平面内容转为3D,再配合陀螺仪将给用户呈现环绕式的沉浸效果。</p> 
         <p>换句话说，手机承担了所有的运算任务和显示任务(因此只有旗舰能胜任)，而VR头盔负责提供一个与隔离的“暗室”，方便用户进入虚拟世界，并且提供部分操控功能。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/d6d0030b707cb246940a5869513ce846.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/d6d0030b707cb246940a5869513ce846.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">透镜部分</span></p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/9bcb4094d89c7d186656b0b9ec12e4c8.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/9bcb4094d89c7d186656b0b9ec12e4c8.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">装入手机</span></p> 
         <p>　　了解完原理，再来看构造就容易多了。Gear VR主要部件就是个插手机的夹子＋两个透镜，夹子支持三星S6之后的旗舰手机，一侧为有识别功能的Micro USB接口，插入手机后可自动进入VR界面，透镜则是定制产品。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/32e8bb0d8306700929359ff3baf64513.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/32e8bb0d8306700929359ff3baf64513.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">侧面触摸板</span></p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/50c0348015771a9b294d2170b17558b0.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/50c0348015771a9b294d2170b17558b0.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">中间黑色部分为距离感应器</span></p> 
         <p>　　VR侧面有触摸板，方便用户操作，并且提供了Micro USB，你可以一边玩一边给手机充电。内侧设置了一个光线感应器，当摘下头盔时候自动关闭屏幕，节约手机功耗。</p> 
         <p>和普通的VR头盔相比，Gear VR主要是贵在这几个细节上。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/6467a5e6448fc5c96309e3cc1500cbd3.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/6467a5e6448fc5c96309e3cc1500cbd3.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">佩戴效果</span></p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/438d579a32f7a1d3be68da2f1c167c9e.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/438d579a32f7a1d3be68da2f1c167c9e.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><strong>　　体验环节：</strong></p> 
         <p>先上两张佩戴图，画风有点怪，不知道是哪里除了问题。</p> 
         <p>佩戴体验，Gear VR很轻，没有沉重的压迫感，稍微勒紧就可以牢固的戴在头上。带眼镜的同学无需摘下眼镜。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/e5be32ac54ae49eed5e4e1986b1ee730.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/e5be32ac54ae49eed5e4e1986b1ee730.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">主界面</span></p> 
         <p>　　Gear VR连接手机后，会提示取下手机安装Oculus(Gear VR平台的内容合作方)，按提示下一步就行，小白也能搞定。但安装之后，需要“科学上网”才能注册帐号，下载软件或者游戏。</p> 
         <p>这一步实在是蛋疼，小编换了好几个vpn才找到能用的，速度仿佛回到了拨号上网时代。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/fd8f6a3b64c6f235d4026aa58534bec4.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/fd8f6a3b64c6f235d4026aa58534bec4.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">游戏界面</span></p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/e6dc9570f22b9c5502a5dbf1c9953e6e.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/e6dc9570f22b9c5502a5dbf1c9953e6e.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">游戏界面</span></p> 
         <p>　　现阶段Oculus平台支持Gear VR的游戏和软件总量在200款左右，游戏占了一半以上，多数为付费，最贵的超过千元，不知道有没有卖出去过，至于免费有序总数不到15款。</p> 
         <p>这里以一款太空射击游戏为例(名字忘了，应该xx船长之类的)，游戏的场景设计在太空，玩家扮演的是飞船的驾驶员，游戏时通过转动头部控制准星，头部向左向右偏来控制飞行方向。</p> 
         <p>操控逻辑非常清晰，上手简单。画面延迟不高，没有出现可恶的头晕呕吐状况，体验值得肯定，有机会一定要试试。</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/2ffe17949bc0904d3633dd9b1b41b71b.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/2ffe17949bc0904d3633dd9b1b41b71b.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">你懂得</span></p> 
         <p><strong>　　看电影怎么样：</strong></p> 
         <p>我知道，很多人是冲着标题点进来的，玩游戏神马的是次要，能不能看羞羞电影才是你们关心的重点。</p> 
         <p>明确告诉大家可以看，但爽不爽和片源有关，主要取决于视频的分辨率，头盔的透镜有放大效果，如果片源分辨率低的话，观看的时候颗粒感会非常明显，看了半天主角到底长啥样你肯能都不知道(别问我哪里有好的片源，我也在找)。</p> 
         <p>但话说回来带着头盔，对着空气..。。画面太美。提醒大家体验的时候一定要找没人的地方哦，另外做事要有个度，否则就像这哥们似的，嗨晕在厕所。</p> 
         <p>如果你有条件的话，建议大家买Oculus加专属外设，这样体验会更上一层楼。</p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><img style="border: black 1px solid;" src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/1204cfba59a3d24f010d99d82ce792dc.gif" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" />
          <noscript>
           <img style="border: black 1px solid;" src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/1204cfba59a3d24f010d99d82ce792dc.gif" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Simsun;">这样玩更爽</span></p> 
         <p>　　最后是Cosplay环节，你们说像不像？</p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/6bd24bc8b572c8e669ae76f15f110577.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/6bd24bc8b572c8e669ae76f15f110577.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <p align="center"><img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/a0e73b35111a002a65c89acac46e91ee.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          <noscript>
           <img src="http://www.vrlei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/a0e73b35111a002a65c89acac46e91ee.jpg" alt="三星Gear VR上手 跟空气啪啪啪真爽！|三星|VR头盔_新浪科技_新浪网" border="1" />
          </noscript></p> 
         <div class="clr"></div> 
        </section> 
